the last night john IMed me and was like YO! lets go to PA tomorrow and get fireworks. of course i was down. well i found out my mom was picking me up from school...FUCK. so i had to find a fireworks store in NH or CT somewher close. he gets here at about 7:15, we hit dunkin donuts and our journy begins. we arrive at Phantom Fireworks (TM). Yah kno? the one advertised on 91north. yeah so we get there and this bitchy lady is like IDENTIFICATION PLEASE. so he shows her and shes like umm scuse me , you gosta be 21 sir. BYE BYE. so we leave and go to walmart which is a few minutes down. we walk around there until we found a victim. john asks this dude to buy us fireworks and he aggrees. so we get to the store again and the people are suspicious. john finds the package he wants, and we are ready to pay. well i go to the car to get the coupons and i see the dude dart out. he comes up to me and hes like sorry guys its wicked unsafe. AND I QUOTE, a grown man say "WICKED UNSAFE" to me. she was on the phone with the cops. oh great. we go back to walmart to look for someone else. we see this "badass" looking guy and we talk to him about buying us some goods. he was an asshole. anyways, we head back home and i decided we should go to CT and see what they have. it wasnt that bad and he bought something neat... buy one get one free so thats always good. then we go to visit my cousin at falcetis and head back to the school. OF COURSE john decides to come in with me...nice this is good. i walk down g hall and guess whos heading right toward me. you got it, MR. WALEN. "boys can i see your passes" john is like im going to guidance but im a senior. great this sets me up. mr.walen is like andy come with me. so hes like im guessing you skipped school with john. we'll have to call your mother about this one. "oh fuck" i think. so we get there and whaddayah know. i get 2 fucking suspensions. GREAT FUN!! oh well thats my day.

have a nice day...asshole.

i will admit, i have made many mistakes in my life. i will admit, i could sit here for hours making excuses to justify myself. i will admit, i sometimes wonder what life would be like if i had made different choices, but thats the past and whats now is now. i need to focus on this whole this with...umm selling candy. it seems like one wrong mistake can lead to another which can lead to another which can lead to this. this is where i am now. beyond a trail of mistakes, no wheres to go now, can't go back. i really can't turn back because of all that i went through to get here. but where can i go from here. there's only forward. forward to what? i don't know where to go. i really need to talk to my phycologist about this. she'll probally tell my mom but i don't care because i gotta figure out where i am going from here. things are going good at home, and i've been hanging out with a lot of long lost friends. but i'm also losing some people that mean a lot to me and i then begin to question myself as to what life do i want to live. its so hard for me to tell what i want to do with my life, but after losing $75 to that kid, i think that woke me up a bit. it IS a shady buisness. if i don't get my money back i am through with this. i might even be through with it even if i do get my money. i don't know, i am so confused right now. i need to stare at a blank screen and get my thoughts straight.

i have no quote. 

SILENCE IS BEAUTIFUL- pj ladd

okay so heres my worst day.

9:00- i woke up for my doctors appointment to the words "GET UP NOW YOU HAVE 15 MINUITES OR I LEAVE AND U ARE GROUNDED". so i manage to get up and i had time for a shower and to get dressed before i was scrambling out the door.

10:40- i get to school just in time for G block with mrs. lynch. i walk in to see shes absent but mrs.frasir was there to tell me i had to see my tutor about my missing school work. oh fuck i didnt do that. we had a great time yelling at me.

12:06- At lunch talking to barrett when brit h comes by to hear the words dealing and smoke in the same sentence. oh great now we have contestant number  1 upset with me.

2:25- go to my house with amanda and bway. we discuss plans.

4:00- i go to some black kids house and wait there for an hour until he comes back. my friend goes to pick up a package from him, he shows him the package, my friend gives him 75 bucks. the kid bounces and doesnt show up. we have the entire neighborhood looking for him. we get to go back tomorrow.

5:30- arrive at the lax game to find out how amanda and brit get into another fight. FIGHT COUNT: 3 for the day. we go to the car to find a note written by brit. oh yey i get to look like a bad person...hmm a real bad person. never seen those words written about me.

GREAT DAY!!!!!
